ine-height:1.65;flex:1">Portafolio digital freelance para cliente del sector geológico. Enfocado en navegación intuitiva y presentación profesional del contenido.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-auto"><span class="tag-pill">UI/UX</span><span class="tag-pill">Web Design</span><span class="tag-pill">Freelance</span></div><div class="h-px w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, #6d28d9, #0891b2)"></div></article></div></div></section><section id="experience" class="section-padding relative"><div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:6rem;right:6rem;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 70%, transparent)"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="mb-14" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><p class="section-label mb-2">04 — Experience</p><h2 style="font-family:Syne, sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1" class="text-white">Experiencia</h2></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="glass-card p-7 group transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1 flex-wrap"><h3 style="font-family:Syne, sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:#e8e8f0;letter-spacing:-0.01em">Desarrollador Freelance</h3><span style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.65rem;padding:0.15rem 0.5rem;border-radius:99px;background:rgba(103,232,249,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(103,232,249,0.2);color:#67e8f9;font-weight:500">2024</span></div><p style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(167,139,250,0.7);margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.02em">Cliente — Sector Geológico</p><p style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(232,232,240,0.5);line-height:1.65">Diseño y desarrollo de portafolio digital personalizado para cliente del sector geológico.</p></div><span style="font-family:Syne, sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:3rem;line-height:1;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);letter-spacing:-0.04em;flex-shrink:0">01</span></div><div class="mt-5 h-px w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed, transparent)"></div></div><div class="glass-card p-7 group transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4"><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1 flex-wrap"><h3 style="font-family:Syne, sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;color:#e8e8f0;letter-spacing:-0.01em">Automatización de Datos</h3><span style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.65rem;padding:0.15rem 0.5rem;border-radius:99px;background:rgba(103,232,249,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(103,232,249,0.2);color:#67e8f9;font-weight:500">2023 — 2024</span></div><p style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(167,139,250,0.7);margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.02em">Proyecto Personal</p><p style="font-family:DM Sans, sans-serif;font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(232,232,240,0.5);line-height:1.65">Scripts Python con Pandas para automatizar reportes de asistencia, reduciendo el tiempo manual en 80%.</p></div><span style="font-family:Syne, sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:3rem;line-height:1;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);letter-spacing:-0.04em;flex-shrink:0">02</span></div><div class="mt-5 h-px w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, #7c3aed, transparent)"></div></div></div></div></section><section id="education" class="section-padding relative"><div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:6rem;right:6rem;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 70%, transpare